## Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

**Is the WhatsApp Business API free?**
No, Meta charges for conversations on the WhatsApp Business API. Charges are based on conversation categories (Marketing, Utility, Authentication, Service). However, the high conversion rate typically results in a very strong ROI compared to traditional channels.

**How do I start with WhatsApp AI?**
You need to partner with an AI automation platform that supports WhatsApp API integration. You will register your business number, build your AI conversational flows, and connect your CRM.

**Does AI really improve lead quality?**
Yes. By instantly asking qualifying questions before a human sales rep ever gets involved, AI ensures that your team only spends time talking to prospects who fit your ideal customer profile and have high buying intent.

**Can WhatsApp AI handle multiple languages?**
Yes, modern LLM-powered AI chatbots can automatically detect the language a user is typing in and respond fluently in that same language, making them perfect for global lead generation campaigns.

